{"tid":1631070,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]對家對連登既滲透日益嚴重，究竟用咩方法係有效??","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T14:43:56.000Z","uid":202426,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9866d415399964b64199d9ebdf7157b9d1c5e856","tid":1631070,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:38:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 集體封鎖相關的帳號</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.禁言，封帳疑似對家既帳號 (呢個要連登哥哥出手</span></strong><br />\n例如同一個帳戶比人封鎖超過3000次 或短時間超過500次，就可以禁言，封帳<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3. 組連登監察隊</span></strong><br />\n監察連登現時風向，以及隔一段時間做對比並分析<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4. 宣傳上連登勿認真既心態</span></strong><br />\n冇大台，所有事靠自己判斷，因為好多時候連登同現實係兩個世界黎。<br />\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n好多時候，連登手足 嘈交都係因為呢個核心問題，<br />\n所以我想講下自己既見解，同埋比大家用睇一個post既時間冷靜下 <br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做，齊上齊落，不割也不分。<br />\n就快4個月啦，應承我要一齊行落去,ok?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXaH4sW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXaH4sW.jpg&h=13467dae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3qY6MGh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3qY6MGh.jpg&h=56dfc8a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12c7383a00e616b67be9dee2389e76bc66067607","tid":1631070,"uid":258696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:38:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家 呢幾日都係行動日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但連登都無比大陸DDos攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就證明左係大量五毛做緊野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又分化又風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我地係時候要醒下<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">跟住就係開始做正經野：<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. 推紅色的士撞人單野<br />\n<br />\n2.推黑警又當街踢人單野<br />\n<br />\n3.九龍塘軍營入面有綠色防暴警既片<br />\n<br />\n4.解釋返裝修既原因比外國知<br />\n<br />\n5.宣傳黑紅藍黃既概念</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地唔好再比五毛搞爆連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"7024884aecd899b81a2b8354a917b9930ff2ddfc","tid":1631070,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252e3d2cfc7c52c373aae31f23c912f58d35fb2a","tid":1631070,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:39:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"742851fd29e6da829ba56784481fa5632d58da54","tid":1631070,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bd661bd84ed561b97325f37931c12e43bc0124","tid":1631070,"uid":202426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm